<br>
The items I can switch out are:<br>
Mamoth Hide Cloak<br>
Reed Belt<br>
Obulous Death Shroud<br>
RMB<br>
forest loop<br>
Velium Ruby Veil<br>
PAW of O in main Melee slot<br>
Platinum Tiara<br>
<br>
<br>
Other slots have:<br>
Nathsar BP and Arms (wouldn't trade for ES if you paid me too)<br>
Black Chitin legs (could only replace with Nathsar or something black and NOT leather. Leather looks awful with the Nathsar.)<br>
Crystal Chitin Shield<br>
Coldain Gloves and Boots<br>
RMBs on both wrists... could replace 1<br>
7 WIS rings<br>
<br>
It needs to be something that can be purchased for 5-6k or quested pretty much solo. I'm in a small guild and don't want to bother them as I'm really new there. I haven't played in a while and I'm not too familiar with a lot of the new stuff... I just about peed myself when I first saw the Nathsar! <br>
<br>
Obviously Nathsar legs would solve all my problems... but I can't seem to find Nathsar legs for sale to save my life and 45 is too low for Chardok!<br>
